The price of crude oil has a direct impact on the demand for turbo diesel engines due to its influence on fuel prices and consumer preferences.

14. What are the technological advancements in turbo diesel engines?
Technological advancements in turbo diesel engines include variable geometry turbochargers, common rail fuel injection systems, and exhaust gas recirculation (EGR) systems.

15. What is the market outlook for turbo diesel engines in the next decade?
The market outlook for turbo diesel engines is positive, driven by increasing demand for commercial vehicles and advancements in engine technology.

